### Create a new booking
POST http://localhost:54666/api/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookingDate": "2024-07-01T14:00:00Z",
  "numberOfSeats": 2
}

### Get a booking by ID (replace {id} with actual booking id from create response)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/bookings/{id}

### Get all bookings (if endpoint exists)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/bookings
